# .env.local — local development environment variables
#
# For PREVIEW MODE (no database needed):
#   These placeholder values let the app start. All preview routes
#   at /preview/* bypass Supabase entirely and use mock data.
#
# For FULL APP (with real database):
#   Replace the three SUPABASE_* values with your real credentials from:
#   https://supabase.com → Your Project → Settings → API

# ── Supabase ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Placeholder values work for /preview/* routes.
# Replace with real values to use /dashboard, /materials, /stock, /cases, etc.
